	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Gratiam et pacem a domino.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum sese mihi ultro offerret presentium lator, volui per eundem, quia michi bonus videbatur, ad te scribere.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nam, ut sunt omnia plena dolis et proditionibus, difficile et plenumque periculis est omnia calami opera significare.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Volui tamen, ut hic praesentium lator tibi esset vice epistole; unde tantum quedam capita significare volui, de quibus ipse coram presentium latori locutus sum; ex hiis poteris pro data tibi prudentia reliqua metiri.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De<note type="misc">vgl. sep. Darstellung des folgenden</note> meo meorumque statu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l320" cert="high">Memminge</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">quibus exactionibus angamur.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">temere dictis cuiusdam <persName type="auto_name">Geldii</persName> contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l457" cert="high">Constanitenses</placeName> in publica mensa <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augustę</placeName> effusis.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">obitu cuiusdam capitanei <persName type="auto_name">Sebastiani Vogelspergii</persName>, quibus mediis in manus lictoris traditus sit, qua constantia animi diem clauserit, deque apologia Caesaries.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">sedecim collocutoribus a Caesare ordinatis.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">commune fama futuri belli, de sestimatione quorundam ad Helvetios.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De promissione <persName ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesaris</persName> duci Sabaudie factis.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De actione inter Caesarem et pontificem super habendo concilio.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">ducatu <placeName ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtenbergensi</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De his omnibus habebis certa ex nunctio.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale in domino, dilecte frater, una cum dilectissima coniuge et charis liberis.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Werden witzig mit frembdem schaden und hand gut acht auff die, so nitt recht am kommet ziehen.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="de"><persName type="auto_name">Pleonexia</persName> ist ein verzweyfflet, verrucht und unverschampte[r] bößwicht;</foreign> nec enim tam ferrea quemquam formavit natura virum, cuius rigor aera sperneret aut nostra foret inpenetrabilis aura etc.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De profectu evangelii in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> forte aliunde tibi notum est.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p2095" cert="high">Philippus Me(lanchthon</persName>) quendam doctum <persName type="auto_name">Hispanum</persName> nunc <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName> agentem<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8032" cert="high">Dryander</persName>; s. z.B. Dry. an HB, 20.3.</note> literis vocavit <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1148" cert="high">Constantinopolim</placeName>; num paruerit vocanti, nondum rescivi.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid multis?</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nobis debebat <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germanis</placeName> primum dei consilio praedicare regnum dei; sed quia bona pars repellimus et indignos nos iudicamus vita aeterna, conversurus est se dominus ad gentes et in transitu est visitator dominus.</s>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Beatus, qui illum fide susceperit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus Iesus Christus corroboret vos ihn suscepta et agnita veritate, avertat a gente vestra omnem imposturam, fraudem et proditionem, donet vos avita fortitudine et integritate, ut possitis in gloriam dei et augmentum veterum virtutum obviare cuivis hosti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta nomine meo uxorem tuam, dominum <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodorum</persName>, <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicanum</persName> et D. <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvaltherum</persName>.</s>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus tecum, mi venerande frater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Datę <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l320" cert="high">Memminge</placeName> 22. februarii anno 1548.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus amicus veteri more tibi notus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heyricho Bullingero</persName>, veteri amico et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
